---
title: Spiced Double Beef and Hummus Bowls with Zucchini, Couscous and Feta
description: This dish is brimming with colour and flavour! Herb-packed tabbouleh, mildly spiced beef and a creamy hummus dressing all come together for a delightful weeknight feast.
